K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-1: a'arya dzvar pra sha ma ni n'a ma dhva ra ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-3: 'phags pa rims nad rab tu zhi bar byed pa ces bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-6: 'od skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-7: bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal na bzhugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-8: de nas dge slong zhig bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te phyogs gcig tu 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-9: phyogs gcig tu 'dug nas dge slong des bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-11: 'di na sems can rnams rims nad kyis gtses par mchis na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285a-14: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-0: phyogs 'di na me lce'i phreng bzhes bya ba'i rims nad @285b 'dug ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-1: sems can rnams la nyin gcig pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-4: nyan bzhi pa la sogs pa la thugs rje dang ldan pas brtse bar byed pas de srung ba'i gsang sngags kyi gzhi rnams 'di dag yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-6: dzva la ni dzva la ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-7: pra ti ba ni pra sha ma ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-8: bdag gi rims nad song zhig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-14: dge 'dun gyi bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig gis bdag gi rims nad song zhig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-16: siddham tu mantra pa t'a ba dha ra bidya na pra ma aa nu mo do sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-17: skud pa nag po la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas shing mdud pa nyi shu gcig bor ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas dge slong de dag yi rang ste bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-032:285b-19: 'phags pa rims nad rab tu zhi bar byed pa'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
